{"tid":228563,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"那些DSE同學所不知道的事－－那些年的A-level數學","createTime":"2017-05-04T03:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T15:53:15.000Z","uid":12599,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"254dc4c00ee41cd8032bfe8372433158b4c5e94f","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"又到公開試的季節，看到同學們為努力讀書，與公開試搏鬥，好不青春。<br />\n<br />\n小弟當年讀的是舊制課程，考的是舊制公開試。據小弟所知，轉了新制後，有研究報告指學生的數理能力持續下降，甚至有大學課程要開enrichment課程，為同學惡補大學所需的數學，好讓他們可以趕得上大學的進度。<br />\n<br />\n當然，小弟不是教育的專家，也不知道轉制對同學數理能力的影響有多大。但起碼從「美學」的角度來說，新制大幅度刪減AL課程，同學的確少了很多機會去接觸一些優美又奧妙的數學課題，又無辨法可以對數學的嚴謹有所認識。相較起DSE數學以運算為主，A-level數學著重的嚴謹的思維與邏輯，及對數學「美學」的觸覺。從一堆看似不相干的數學結果中推論出優美的新結論，那種快樂及滿足感是純粹做運算無可比擬的。對小弟來說，DSE的數學是「工匠」的數學，AL的數學是「藝術家」的數學（雖然也只是很初階的「藝術家」數學）。<br />\n<br />\n即使以實用性來說，A-level數學的複數、圓錐曲線、微分方程等也是科學、工程，甚至是金融經濟中必不可少的數學工具。<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟突然有感而發，想跟大家分享一下舊制的數學課程，並給大家看一下當年的試題，感受一下當年的數學之美。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的A-level，全稱Advanced level，有兩科數學科，分別是Pure Mathematics（純粹數學）及Applied Mathematics（應用數學）。另外有一科AS-level（Advanced Supplementary Level）的Mathematics and statistics（數學及統計學），AS-level相等如半科的A-level，所以課程簡單得多，比較貼近今天DSE數學的M1，小弟就不在此多討論了。<br />\n<br />\nPure Mathematics分兩份卷，卷一是代數，卷二是微積分。<br />\n<br />\n當年Pure Mathematics難到最多同學，但同時也是最美及最巧妙的課題，自然是inequalities。這個課題非常考同學的數學觸覺，可惜今天的同學已經無機會接觸到AM-GM inequality、Cauchy-Schwarz inequality等大名鼎鼎的數學不等式。以下是一題當年典型的inequalities題目：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7d0Wq9oUWb8/WP4A6HY1rLI/AAAAAAAAAoE/C0eVrbSGPaAONWZCf5XyqlCHp3BoXmtMwCLcB/s1600/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-7d0Wq9oUWb8%2FWP4A6HY1rLI%2FAAAAAAAAAoE%2FC0eVrbSGPaAONWZCf5XyqlCHp3BoXmtMwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&h=d738c9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個消失了的大課題是complex number（複數），今天的DSE課程只是約略地談及複數的運算，已經沒有了Argand diagram、De Moivre&rsquo;s theorem等重要概念，須知道這兩個概念甚至在再舊一點的時代甚至只是會學程度（中五程度）的課題。Complex number在科學計算中是非常有用的工具，電學、波動學，甚至量子力學都會見到它們的影子。單從數學來說，它也是我們分析高次方程及三角函數的有用工具。把複數結合三角函數，往往會得出一些意想不到的巧妙結果：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MORtt5xBvjQ/WP4BGlRJauI/AAAAAAAAAoI/0HRlJ1zZvGYPF6O_UgYuQoAdhCszQ8k6QCLcB/s1600/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-MORtt5xBvjQ%2FWP4BGlRJauI%2FAAAAAAAAAoI%2F0HRlJ1zZvGYPF6O_UgYuQoAdhCszQ8k6QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&h=ff420efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下是一題很精彩的高次方程問題，分析高次方程的實數根的數量，當中也隱隱地滲透一點複數的概念：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-szpi8iErS8E/WP4BV7B_AcI/AAAAAAAAAoM/2qKLImWqLTg8haX1U5MHUWvnjNvdNNr1QCLcB/s1600/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-szpi8iErS8E%2FWP4BV7B_AcI%2FAAAAAAAAAoM%2F2qKLImWqLTg8haX1U5MHUWvnjNvdNNr1QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F3.jpg&h=7752247f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbf9193b958f0a8738eacf37204e9091dbf0ac2b","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"至於卷二的微積分，其實當中的運算大多都不複雜，但同學一定要對基本的微積分概念，如limit、differentiability、continuity、fundamental theorem of calculus，甚至是微分及積分的定義都有透徹的了解，不是「計到就算」。可以就，這份卷可以讓同學淺嚐數學一門分支──analysis的威力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-liyxdI-sno8/WQN4Un4jusI/AAAAAAAAAoc/RNm2l3FwD3QWicQsk9pd5qWD_7u0LDxqwCLcB/s1600/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-liyxdI-sno8%2FWQN4Un4jusI%2FAAAAAAAAAoc%2FRNm2l3FwD3QWicQsk9pd5qWD_7u0LDxqwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F4.jpg&h=96ebd74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lbgWUJDMRIw/WQN4cWNeaLI/AAAAAAAAAog/0Cfo-nDSnXQWRb59zIXtYKTwQG1a-0-fACLcB/s1600/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-lbgWUJDMRIw%2FWQN4cWNeaLI%2FAAAAAAAAAog%2F0Cfo-nDSnXQWRb59zIXtYKTwQG1a-0-fACLcB%2Fs1600%2F5.jpg&h=91920763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GvEM3TAxjOM/WQN4qA4aUJI/AAAAAAAAAok/TDjlNr0llt0qm8LdEIfrM3viAuVDrkNrACLcB/s1600/6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-GvEM3TAxjOM%2FWQN4qA4aUJI%2FAAAAAAAAAok%2FTDjlNr0llt0qm8LdEIfrM3viAuVDrkNrACLcB%2Fs1600%2F6.jpg&h=a7a69d10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f35dba721b1ce2bfc1432821a71d061aaa07423","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"至於Applied Math，當年應考的同學不多，大家對它的認識也應該不太深。先談談卷二，卷二有三大課題，分別是微分方程、數值分法，及概率與統計。三個課題都異常地實用，在物理、化學、醫學，甚至生態學、傳染病學、經濟學、金融學。特別是微分方程，引入這個課題簡直是為一絕，可以說是為同學通往高階科學開了一對門，引入一線光。小弟很難用三言兩語說得明白微分方程在科學中有多重要，但真的，懂科學的人自然懂微分方程有多重要。以下是當年的幾題微分方程題目：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-auDCUsULYwI/WQN47na0ulI/AAAAAAAAAoo/b_BAUZqNxRM0s_fq2TsQLRGkAVwtZGleQCLcB/s1600/7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-auDCUsULYwI%2FWQN47na0ulI%2FAAAAAAAAAoo%2Fb_BAUZqNxRM0s_fq2TsQLRGkAVwtZGleQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F7.jpg&h=43c3deaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-g7j7_vZT4YI/WQN5L4k_EII/AAAAAAAAAos/D34VIbyEwQMSyaqGb_Cl6vspJQ51FSVjgCLcB/s1600/8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-g7j7_vZT4YI%2FWQN5L4k_EII%2FAAAAAAAAAos%2FD34VIbyEwQMSyaqGb_Cl6vspJQ51FSVjgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F8.jpg&h=192dcec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數值方法可被視為合法的「出貓」，有很多數學問題，基本上都是不可能給出確實的答案。但數值方法是非常有用的數學工具，令我們可以求出一個非常接近答案的近似值。<br />\n<br />\n以下是一題Newton's method的典型題目。當年小弟在考會考時遇到不典型的方程式時，也很愛「出貓」用Newton's method幫手找個數值答案，按計數機幾下就找到答案，不用甚麼腦力（雖然這方法不在會考課程中）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-80hjHKYSUq8/WQN5dOiCeHI/AAAAAAAAAow/jJVScfNa0i8Q0kv6JW2nQWVlut84R3RFwCLcB/s1600/9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-80hjHKYSUq8%2FWQN5dOiCeHI%2FAAAAAAAAAow%2FjJVScfNa0i8Q0kv6JW2nQWVlut84R3RFwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F9.jpg&h=dd4a5b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTaylor series又是另一個重要的數值方法：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xf9SC3YMRxA/WQN5nSoGciI/AAAAAAAAAo0/p2IG1Qs6UcwkuKhvdTTVjd_N3kzeDIW9QCLcB/s1600/10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-xf9SC3YMRxA%2FWQN5nSoGciI%2FAAAAAAAAAo0%2Fp2IG1Qs6UcwkuKhvdTTVjd_N3kzeDIW9QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F10.jpg&h=614079ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"963c183b7cf3d23b8700c76a77250f6963f08edb","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"最後才談Applied Math卷一，小弟一直覺得卷一是一份非常神奇的卷。它根本不是一份數學卷，而是一份撤頭徹尾的物理卷，考的是力學。但它考的力學自然比「正規」物理卷難得多，而且也要大量用到微分方程等的數學工具。其實，力學也確實是一個需要大量數學應用的領域。其實會考程度的Applied Maths也曾經在八十年代之前有過一份paper 3是考力學的試卷，可見力學曾經也是中學數學的一個重要元素。可惜到今天，力學已經全面退出數學的舞台。<br />\n<br />\n下面是一題SHM（簡諧運動，simple harmonic motion）的題目。可惜到今天，不但數學課程裡看不到它的蹤影，就連物理課程都不再教了，鳴呼哀哉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-PmNU-dKK4jA/WQN53fEzoQI/AAAAAAAAAo4/wDdATGfwx5ozRrYpwLmJKGdIr4zmWcIDwCLcB/s1600/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-PmNU-dKK4jA%2FWQN53fEzoQI%2FAAAAAAAAAo4%2FwDdATGfwx5ozRrYpwLmJKGdIr4zmWcIDwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F11.jpg&h=d15ab53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，送多一題projectile motion及一題circular motion的問題給大家：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6V-tea52dkU/WQN6I4T45hI/AAAAAAAAAo8/w6AcLUc9uSgMGUkc_4JTJwBQjuov6cldwCLcB/s1600/12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6V-tea52dkU%2FWQN6I4T45hI%2FAAAAAAAAAo8%2Fw6AcLUc9uSgMGUkc_4JTJwBQjuov6cldwCLcB%2Fs1600%2F12.jpg&h=2da8f721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WqHJrcu0V0U/WQN6TJ9tWqI/AAAAAAAAApA/dxUzIcDn5nkcrvXJZkwYPeKY0IRoaWTuQCLcB/s1600/13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-WqHJrcu0V0U%2FWQN6TJ9tWqI%2FAAAAAAAAApA%2FdxUzIcDn5nkcrvXJZkwYPeKY0IRoaWTuQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F13.jpg&h=4e083ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文及solution:<br />\n<a href=\"http://drstanford.blogspot.hk/2017/04/dsea-level.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrstanford.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F04%2Fdsea-level.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b1835c56\" target=\"_blank\">http://drstanford.blogspot.hk/2017/04/dsea-level.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"6dbabe0a852ffad5a1ab862691022a194f330d6d","tid":228563,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係讀Maths <br />\n但而家唸返起個陣A level <br />\n真係唔知點解自己可以捱得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：個陣讀Account 同business studies <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b026f054e13327a8eacf35d067fe1085c83898e8","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然唔係讀Maths <br />\n但而家唸返起個陣A level <br />\n真係唔知點解自己可以捱得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：個陣讀Account 同business studies <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我當年applied maths同pure maths 20年past paper各做左2次<br />\n<br />\n最後一科B一科C,屌出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9debd0c5b61ad40a06161a022d3f9424fada1046","tid":228563,"uid":29040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"數學白痴engin仔表示全部都好似唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09efa878d7c0c02a90c13a6576cc6dbaab4cf308","tid":228563,"uid":76637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"好文一推"},{"pid":"4d919e9c548e7eb319541e3d0236391a425f1d20","tid":228563,"uid":92628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然唔係讀Maths <br />\n但而家唸返起個陣A level <br />\n真係唔知點解自己可以捱得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：個陣讀Account 同business studies <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我當年applied maths同pure maths 20年past paper各做左2次<br />\n<br />\n最後一科B一科C,屌出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日覺得讀得applied maths 本身都係精英中的精英<br />\n你pure phy 坐底al c 先會去試applied maths <br />\n拉curve下自然好殘酷，總有精英為精英中的精英墊底<br />\n<br />\n總結係，bio 人覺得 applied maths 唔抵讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa3e3248c021c0461dfeb2293b10fbd0d400f47","tid":228563,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然唔係讀Maths <br />\n但而家唸返起個陣A level <br />\n真係唔知點解自己可以捱得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：個陣讀Account 同business studies <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEcon business Applied Math<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63711337f4ed917596ace082b0b6ecd1e387299a","tid":228563,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8957c6648b8ff8656fc245e5936864b506115577","tid":228563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"